name: Razor Spark Skooter
description: The Razor Spark scooter is a sleek and fun ride, perfect for kids who want an extra spark of excitement. Equipped with a spark bar, it creates real sparks as you ride, adding a cool visual effect. It's lightweight, easy to fold, and features a sturdy aluminum frame, making it durable yet portable. The rear fender brake ensures safe and smooth stopping, while the adjustable handlebars make it comfortable for riders of different heights.
